## Fail closed (data integrity guardrails)

**Never save production panel or cold-tier data without passing invariants.**

| Gate | Where enforced |
|------|----------------|
| Panel invariants | `panel_invariants.assert_panel_invariants` ‚Üí `save_panel` (blocks promote) |
| Audit script | `scripts/audit_prediction_data.py --days 500` exits 1 on invariant failure |
| CI | `scripts/verify_prediction_pipeline.py` runs audit + `tests/test_history_panel.py` |

Rules:

1. **No join that drops daily columns** ‚Äî annual/weekly joins fill NaN only; `ANNUAL_JOIN_BLOCKLIST` excludes `usd_inr` from annual join entirely.
2. **No full-replace cold-tier save** when merge can preserve existing rows ‚Äî use `merge=True` or `merge_with_priority`.
3. **No panel save without WAP** ‚Äî stage ‚Üí invariant check ‚Üí promote; previous generation kept as `{name}.previous.parquet`.
4. **Force bypass only intentionally** ‚Äî `INDEX_PANEL_SAVE_FORCE=1` or `--force` on materialize script; log in manifest.
5. **PRs touching** `history_panel.py`, `history_store.py`, `history_ingest.py`, `panel_enrichment.py` must update `tests/test_history_panel.py` or invariant tests.

Implementation: [`panel_invariants.py`](integrations/trade_integrations/dataflows/index_research/panel_invariants.py), [`COLUMN_GRANULARITY`](integrations/trade_integrations/dataflows/index_research/panel_invariants.py).
